description: A collection of circles in a large square formation turned slightly so that the corners of the formation are at the top, bottom, left, and right sides of the picture; there is also a very thin line of circles extending upwards from the top side of the formation. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a greenish-blue triangle toward the right corner of the formation.

author.name: VertexArchive
